Well this giant pied girl has never really liked me 🤷‍♂️ and in this video she finally gets me 😬 not only is she super mom defending her eggs 🥚 but she is only one generation from a wild snake 🐍 making her genes a little more crazy 🧬 regardless she’s a beautiful snake and her babies will be even prettier 😍 
.
.
.

node.text:
MyLove is one of the most beautiful snakes in the 🌍 and looks incredible with the sun hitting her just right ☀️ she’s also the best tempered snake I’ve ever had 😊 so when @sofiedossi asked me to bring her to put her on a blind folded friend we made it happen 🤜 
.
.
.

node.text:
It seems Tripod is everyone’s favorite croc 🐊 and I don’t blame anyone because he’s incredible 😎 looking forward to hopefully visiting him and @mattwright again in the future 😬 but it’s pretty incredible how big that tooth is 😱 the cool thing is just like a shark 🦈 crocs never stop growing back new ones 🦷 so a replacement is coming in right behind this one ☝️ 
.
.
.

Hatching baby pythons is always exciting 🎉 but even more exciting when they’re so rare and look so incredible 😱 these snakes have all sorts of combined genes 🧬 found from the wild and selectively bred to make these amazing snakes 🐍 they look like no other pieds and almost look like leopards 🐆 they’re absolutely beautiful and can’t wait to watch them grow up 🙏
.
.
.

When the big reticulated pythons lay their eggs 🥚 the best thing for the babies and the mom is to remove the eggs 🤷‍♂️ this is because the babies get a higher chance at successfully hatching 🐣 and the mom gets to go back to her normal life quicker 🐍 of course mama doesn’t know I’m trying to help 😬 which can make it interesting 😂 
.
.
.

node.text:
It seems Tripod is everyone’s favorite croc 🐊 and I don’t blame anyone because he’s incredible 😎 looking forward to hopefully visiting him and @mattwright again in the future 😬 but it’s pretty incredible how big that tooth is 😱 the cool thing is just like a shark 🦈 crocs never stop growing back new ones 🦷 so a replacement is coming in right behind this one ☝️ 
.
.
.
#animals #reptiles #dinosaur #crocodile #saltwatercrocodile #croc #australia #prehistoric #prehistoricanimals #igtv #igtvchannel #igtvvideo #insta #style
